article.description: — Luis Kortright, Tymu Chenery and Jacob Rigoni scored 18 points apiece as Quinnipiac beat Rider 80-64 on Saturday.
article.headline: Quinnipiac defeats Rider 80-64
article.story: HAMDEN, Conn. -- — Luis Kortright, Tymu Chenery and Jacob Rigoni scored 18 points apiece as Quinnipiac beat Rider 80-64 on Saturday. Rigoni also had 15 rebounds for his third double-double this season. Tyrese Williams added 11 points for Quinnipiac (7-9, 5-7 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Dwight Murray Jr. had 16 points for the Broncs (4-12, 4-9). Christian Ings added 12 points and seven rebounds. Allen Powell had 10 points as did Ajiri Ogemuno-Johnson. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com ------
